dels such as $\\Lambda$CDM. To perform these\ncomputations, we use an implementation of TMNRE via the open-source code\n\\texttt{swyft}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Nov 2021 19:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2022 15:38:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
