ing the proposed global corrections\nto entail fast convergence rate. Extensive experiments on real-world datasets\nshow that LLCG can significantly improve the efficiency without hurting the\nperformance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2021 03:07:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Nov 2021 17:06:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 7 Dec 2021 16:55:20 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 13 Mar 2022 14:51:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-15"}
