ts which affect the\nshape of the heavy fragments is the key reason for the decreasing energy\ndependence of the average TKE of the fission fragments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2021 07:56:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-08"}
