 interest are the ones flowing in\nthe other quantum dot. Remarkably, in this situation we find that non-local\nrectification can be perfect as a consequence of the fact that the heat\ncurrents vanish for properly tuned parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2021 10:44:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Nov 2021 13:51:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2022 13:56:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-11"}
