at\nof the hybrid functional HSE06. ZnO, a long-standing challenge case for DFT+U,\nis addressed by means of Zn 4s instead of Zn 3d correction, in which case the\nfirst-principles DFT+U+J band-gap error is half of that reported for HSE06.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2021 14:05:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-17"}
