idence for the formation of acetaldehyde\n(CH$_3$CHO) and possible formation of ethanol (CH$_3$CH$_2$OH), two COM\nderivatives of CH$_2$CO hydrogenation. The underlying reaction network is\npresented and the astrochemical implications of the derived pathways are\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2021 15:22:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-26"}
